  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE THE MOST INCONVENIENT WAY TO SERVE CUSTOMERS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/6d54c5e5d5b4c472fefab5ebd1feeeec.poster.avif?t=1657112286\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/6d54c5e5d5b4c472fefab5ebd1feeeec.webm?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/6d54c5e5d5b4c472fefab5ebd1feeeec.mp4?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Feed the customers of a restaurant using a set of weird machines attached to a conveyor belt!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER MULTI-TASKING EYE-HAND COORDINATION</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/2669527d018eb0ccf7d54ccdf19b9447.poster.avif?t=1657112286\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/2669527d018eb0ccf7d54ccdf19b9447.webm?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/2669527d018eb0ccf7d54ccdf19b9447.mp4?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>React at the right time to feed the customers while keeping an eye on the timer, the orders, the clients and the dishes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENDURE SHORT SESSIONS OF FAST PACED GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/115cab83b623862da96de939914fc3ae.poster.avif?t=1657112286\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/115cab83b623862da96de939914fc3ae.webm?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/115cab83b623862da96de939914fc3ae.mp4?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Complete each of the 70 level's objective in 45 seconds. The conveyor belt who brings the food won't slow down, so your brain has to speed up!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DISCOVER MECHANICS THAT BRINGS NEW BRAIN-MELTING CHALLENGES</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/d5cb031cf60380c1995ada57d56a5c76.poster.avif?t=1657112286\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/d5cb031cf60380c1995ada57d56a5c76.webm?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/d5cb031cf60380c1995ada57d56a5c76.mp4?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Learn to use ingenious machines that might reveal themselves as more difficult than you expected at first sight!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FOCUS TO SURVIVE AN OVERWHELMINGLY TENSE LEVELS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/8dbd062de95ae09d5cf60d3e7b9a9412.poster.avif?t=1657112286\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/8dbd062de95ae09d5cf60d3e7b9a9412.webm?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636070/extras/8dbd062de95ae09d5cf60d3e7b9a9412.mp4?t=1657112286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Stress test your nerves, your logic and your reflexes in many different ways. Strap in because it's going to be a bumpy ride!<br><br>",
